The Down Quark · node ATM · ATM · The up quark's partner — fundamental, fractionally charged. Protons hold one; neutrons hold two.

universe of origin : ATM · The Atom
seal               : DECIDES PROTON vs NEUTRON. Swapping one down-quark for an up (via the weak force) turns a neutron into a proton — that's beta decay, the engine of radioactivity and of how stars build elements.
